text: Louis Seigneur was a Canadian politician. In the 10 August 1958 federal election, he unsuccessfully sought election in Quebec East riding as a Locataire (Tenant) candidate. He won 417 votes, 1.3% of the popular vote. ==See also== *List of political parties in Canada ==Sources== *Parliament of Canada History of the Federal Electoral Ridings since 1867 Category:Federal political parties in Canada
title: Louis Seigneur
